Privacy Policy for News App (No User Information Collection)

Effective Date: 1 Jun 2023

This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle user information for our news application ("App") that does not collect any personal information or user data. We respect your privacy and are committed to maintaining the confidentiality of any information you do not provide while using our App.

No Collection of Personal Information:
We do not collect or store any personal information about you while you use our App. We have designed our App to operate without requiring any user registration, login, or data input. Therefore, we do not collect your name, email address, location, or any other personally identifiable information.

No Usage Information Collection:
We do not collect any usage information about your activities within the App. We do not use cookies, analytics, or any other tracking technologies to monitor or record your interactions with our App.

No Information Sharing:
Since we do not collect any user information, we have no user data to share with third parties. We do not disclose any information to service providers, advertisers, or any other external entities.

Data Security:
While we do not collect any user information, we still employ reasonable security measures to protect the App's infrastructure and prevent unauthorized access or breaches. We strive to ensure the security and integrity of our systems to maintain user trust.

Children's Privacy:
Our App is suitable for users of all ages, including children. We do not knowingly collect any personal information from individuals under the age of 16. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child, we will promptly delete it from our records.

Changes to the Privacy Policy:
In the event that we decide to change our privacy practices, we will update this Privacy Policy accordingly. However, since we do not collect any user information, any updates will primarily focus on clarifying our non-data collection stance. We recommend periodically reviewing this Privacy Policy for any changes.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy practices or this Privacy Policy, please contact us using the information provided in the App or on our website.

Please note that this Privacy Policy only applies to our App's functionalities and practices related to user information collection. If you interact with third-party websites or services through our App, their privacy policies will govern the collection, use, and disclosure of your information on those platforms.

Thank you for using our news App, and we appreciate your trust in our commitment to privacy.
